h3 We want to set some credentials so we can store your plan on different devices.

h4
  p: input(type="text", ng-model="model.email", placeholder="Email")
  p: input(type="text", ng-model="model.password", placeholder="Password")
  p: small We are showing you a password, so you remember what you entered.

h4
  button(ng-click="attempt(model.createUser())") OK, move on
